VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT %@\s?Page\s?.*\s?ValidateRequest\s?=\s?(\'|\")false(\'|\")
WHEN EXPR PRESENT:validateRequest\s*=\s*"false"|ValidateInput\s*\(\s*false|RequestValidationMode && MISSING:test|example|AntiXssEncoder|HtmlEncode
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects the disabled configuration of request validation in ASP.NET Web Forms, which may lead to security vulnerabilities.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Request Validation: Disabled Configuration.
